---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { fetchData } from "../../utils/fetchData";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import myImage from "../../assets/img/about.jpg";
import "../../css/about.css";

const { info } = await fetchData(Astro.url);
---

<Layout title={info.common.menu.about + " Us"}>
  <div id="aboutPage" class="content" data-invalidate="1">
    <div class="img-logo">
      <div class="box img">
        <div class="automation">
          <Image
            src={myImage}
            alt="Automation Background"
            width={400}
            height={400}
            loading="eager"
            quality="mid"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="box logo-bottom">
        <div class="icon-common-endalogo svg-image"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <div class="box about">
        <h1>About <strong>ENDA</strong></h1>
        <p>
          Sisel Engineering Inc., headquartered in Istanbul, was founded by 4
          engineers in 1989 for the purpose of marketing sensors, control
          devices &amp; transmitters related to measurement of
          physicalÂ parameters (such as temperature, humidity, pressure, and flow
          rate, level) and offering related engineering services. Encouraged by
          the achievements in 1992, the Company started production in the field
          of industrial electronics using ENDA trade mark.
        </p>

        <p>
          By the virtue of its dealer network, the Company is able to provide
          the machinery manufacturers and industrial plants which constitute the
          power of industry, with customer focused solutions. The company also
          increases the productivity of companies and contributes them in
          realizing their targets.
        </p>

        <p>
          We are in the same business for 28 years and our development is due
          primarily to the importance placed on R&amp;D and investments on
          technology. For increasing our share in the market, we shall continue
          doing investments.
        </p>

        <p>
          In 2009 September, the company has also started to do business in
          Lighting Systems and Control area. With our experienced and dynamic
          team, we are providing technical and architectural lighting system
          solutions, as well as lighting automation systems for indoor and
          outdoor lighting projects.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Services</h2>
        We are providing a portfolio of services along the entire manufacturing-consult-design-build-operate-maintain
        cycle regarding the Industrial Automation and Lighting systems.
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Values</h2>
        What make our services indispensable are our services: We are with you at
        any time with our lighting solutions defining &quot;Efficiency, Energy Saving,
        Aesthetics, High Technology, and Quality.&quot;
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Vision</h2>
        To be a pioneering company as a first choice which is driving the changes
        in the Industrial Automation and Lighting Systems sector.
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Mission</h2>
        To manufacture customer oriented, highly technologic, eco and qualified products
        with a sense of continuous improvement and innovation.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
